{"tid":1357600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂][全部同我入黎] 屌你老母全部同我入黎呀 講講講 講撚完未呀？醒未呀？","createTime":"2019-07-23T18:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T18:19:22.000Z","uid":144279,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"376ebd5b09cd95a3e587a4db81f25f56220772b2","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:05:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三十六槍呀<br />\n亂尻咁射呀<br />\n冇預警開槍呀<br />\n有手足被人爆頭呀 係生係死都未知呀<br />\n班仆街一句都冇交代過個三十六槍呀</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gm2c5AA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgm2c5AA.png&h=1bcce7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wiGYVB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wiGYVB.png&h=38a707ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成班淨係係到講元朗乜乜乜元朗乜乜乜 <br />\n唔係話元朗單野唔重要 我都好撚嬲呀<br />\n但係我地唔可以比呢單野蒙蔽咗我地雙眼架<br />\n你地記唔記得我地係為咗啲咩而出黎呀 被人打個嘅義士係因為咩而比人打呀？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係我地一開次要求嘅五大訴求呀！！<br />\n係我地一開次要求嘅五大訴求呀！！<br />\n係我地一開次要求嘅五大訴求呀！！<br />\n係我地一開次要求嘅五大訴求呀！！<br />\n係我地一開次要求嘅五大訴求呀！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醒喇好唔好呀我求吓你地<br />\n我地主要目標係呢個爛臭閪政府<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵人係呢個爛臭閪政府呀<br />\n敵人係呢個爛臭閪政府呀<br />\n敵人係呢個爛臭閪政府呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n君子報仇 十年未晚 我地今次嘅運動成功咗 要再同班牛屎佬算帳都未遲架<br />\n我唔想大家因爲元朗單野而令到場運動有負面影響甚至失敗呀 如果真係嘅話你地對唔對得住自己同我地嘅手足呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你對唔對得住佢？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UznJnR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UznJnR.png&h=a977dae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢呢？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xuu3sPH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuu3sPH.png&h=039fdbb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對唔對得住佢呀？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CQSsUuV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCQSsUuV.png&h=9b820dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有佢呀！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bixku3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbixku3q.png&h=fa63e247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以令佢地失望架 ！！<br />\n因為元朗而比政府轉移視線搞到失敗咗仲對唔對得住自己良心呀！！<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拜托大家唔好再失焦落去 再咁落去會散架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzjfiXj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpzjfiXj.png&h=9db0bd94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tstr930.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTstr930.png&h=962fbf2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2322838f35903f9dca4bcdd4ef60c12f71457d8f","tid":1357600,"uid":144849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:06:55.000Z","msg":"一句到尾入唔入元朗唔入即係鬼"},{"pid":"ecd53aeacefe5078f7ab244415fad9f7e4e82093","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2322838f35903f9dca4bcdd4ef60c12f71457d8f","tid":1357600,"uid":144849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:06:55.000Z","msg":"一句到尾入唔入元朗唔入即係鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"入就入撚梗 但我希望大家都唔好唔記得我地為乜野而出黎"},{"pid":"a9a58941fbfafa10ce50379c9593c710f208a99e","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2519aef1f7d9943972ad8037f59cc5f725c8d788","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:10:53.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"ef74e9a5268df8f4e8f51452906831bd58e56553","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"891d713c6463d5de2edde18b6095cc2bb85acf98","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:11:22.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"93fd62b463299cb7f74b2b64bdb0745bd3ba3cd6","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:11:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76964cef38bd5e136bc25750dba71156af392030","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a488b6367152c014323a2386b89a5c378b5534b1","tid":1357600,"uid":139501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:14:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比太多無謂野spin左focus"},{"pid":"ebcbcc54197e97145e2b04f93fc94a1c6d5d3e81","tid":1357600,"uid":256067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:14:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上環元朗兩邊都重要，但希望上環情況多啲啲文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申兩邊都要文宣，仲要喺連登以外更加要，<span style=\"color: red;\">無連登嘅朋友多數淨係知元朗啲嘢</span>，感覺上偏咗啲去元朗，可能比較切身大眾市民，上環清場方法嚴重性都好大，仲未講喺中聯辦嗰到讀嘅宣言同五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a842459bfac3bc2f5f307e0c82ea2e5f70e5f5da","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:14:33.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"9a3c2452227c81c20f0b6493ba7a7a322a87cd50","tid":1357600,"uid":231594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:14:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"302a1625f6e8a668fa3b734b4432cbf6a819d08e","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:15:08.000Z","msg":"推呀 上熱門呀"},{"pid":"4594eb4fdf2cbc23decc917ae2fbb74b75c8e55f","tid":1357600,"uid":173949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:16:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7384b7c7e3ad28cc0f3df51f6762d1b60d4e83d3","tid":1357600,"uid":173949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:16:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"942ebf97dbf9af5c799591d4826c359ad3ad2c78","tid":1357600,"uid":173949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:17:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e9da9c39a04b4e00ca114d28b7e712462bcdbdc1","tid":1357600,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:17:13.000Z","msg":"兄弟各爬山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港不應成為黑警天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1。推行真雙普選<br />\n2。成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n3。停止搜捕示威者<br />\n4。白紙黑字除消612暴動定義<br />\n5。撤回送中條例<br />\n6。徹查警黑勾結<br />\n7。徹查警察濫暴"},{"pid":"91f38eef9e1d68170b779781e9b7cf519a5051b6","tid":1357600,"uid":173949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f5c2ccd54ab8ff1900bf776f2afab43ac86cd26b","tid":1357600,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecd53aeacefe5078f7ab244415fad9f7e4e82093","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2322838f35903f9dca4bcdd4ef60c12f71457d8f","tid":1357600,"uid":144849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:06:55.000Z","msg":"一句到尾入唔入元朗唔入即係鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"入就入撚梗 但我希望大家都唔好唔記得我地為乜野而出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"元朗單野係西環中聯辦直接指揮<br />\n嚴重性同埋潛在傷害遠超同一夜西環<br />\n<br />\n星期六唔收佢皮 佢星期日就會派黑社會去到港島等你<br />\n<br />\n出到黑社會即係佢已經冇人 外強中乾"},{"pid":"2e50a06f2b529a55dcd548b7d0930c39247ba65e","tid":1357600,"uid":173949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:17:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dba387bb283f0a689ee4d0e0a6d359a334e14cfc","tid":1357600,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"如果大家可以幫手推幾吓喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好令大家忘記初衷呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}